Write the constructor method in the NurbsSurface class.
Remember to respond with a snippet in the form of the following:
```
class NurbsSurface {
    constructor(degreeU, degreeV, controlPoints, knotsU, knotsV, weights) {
        // your code here
    }
}
```

```javascript
class NurbsSurface {
    constructor(degreeU, degreeV, controlPoints, knotsU, knotsV, weights) {
        this.degreeU = degreeU;
        this.degreeV = degreeV;
        this.controlPoints = controlPoints;
        this.knotsU = knotsU;
        this.knotsV = knotsV;
        this.weights = weights;
    }
}
```
